  "sections": {
    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "TTP or ecchymosis on the palmar bony surface is highly suggestive of fracture\nLoss of the normal knuckle contour\nDue to dorsal angulation of fracture apex due to pull of the interosseous muscles",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
